## Honest revised baseline (27B-3.5 DFlash LRU max=120)

| Variant | tok/s | τ |
|---|---|---|
| Single-blank prompt (canonical "max-perf") | **184** ± 15 | **9.42** |
| Double-blank prompt (PEP-8 strict) | **161** ± 2 | **8.07** |
| Fibonacci prompt (max=120) | 119 | 5.40 |
| Has_close_elements prompt | 133 | 6.39 |
